          "port": "8080",
          "path": [
            "api",
            "v1",
            "restaurants"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Create a new restaurant in the database.\n\nExpected Response: HTTP 201 Created\nResponse will include the created restaurant with auto-generated ID"
